l/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35f5d3da3f584e1467886078608b9bd2d435a86","tid":796744,"uid":197602,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"yelo最正"},{"pid":"2978f44b1c04b5a201d7d0f091b74f7150a23a1b","tid":796744,"uid":67778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"啊精正d定杜小喬正d(正版對番版）"},{"pid":"6ac29e79b693b24d648ed533d2ba9459d83fe4f5","tid":796744,"uid":162978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"rachel"},{"pid":"c4146f74639e3f49616d14d9130262de15ce562f","tid":796744,"uid":72629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2624a7b2c7f9d2502c845faf2ca499d2c7b89145","tid":796744,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a4e95740e6773be4acc194ed7898121e0308e655","tid":796744,"uid":147923,"like":22,"dislike":15,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"Sulin 一開始都覺得正<br />\n睇耐左個臉型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRosalina <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n得rosalina先係真靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:07:47.000Z